article.description: — Dameane Douglas posted 16 points and eight rebounds as Loyola Marymount easily beat Cal Poly 76-52 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Douglas, Scott carry Loyola Marymount over Cal Poly 76-52
article.linkText: Douglas, Scott carry Loyola Marymount over Cal Poly 76-52
article.story: LOS ANGELES -- — Dameane Douglas posted 16 points and eight rebounds as Loyola Marymount easily beat Cal Poly 76-52 on Saturday night. Eli Scott added 16 points and six assists for the Lions, and Mattias Markusson chipped in 13 points. Camren Pierce had 10 points for the Mustangs (2-4). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
